WEBVTT

00:03.270 --> 00:06.470
A raid is a large-scale battle

00:06.470 --> 00:09.990
with many adventurers, 
instead of the usual party of six.

00:11.990 --> 00:15.080
The most common type is called a "Full Raid,"

00:14.340 --> 00:18.400
<b>Full Raid</b>

00:15.080 --> 00:18.410
and involves twenty-four players, 
in four groups of six.

00:19.150 --> 00:21.910
It comes with all the fun of a large-scale battle.

00:24.260 --> 00:27.980
A raid requires more than high 
levels and good equipment.

00:28.510 --> 00:31.010
You must analyze the opponent and form a plan,

00:31.330 --> 00:35.010
and players must work together 
to carry out that plan.

00:36.450 --> 00:38.600
You aren't just a random group of people.

00:39.820 --> 00:42.770
The most important element 
is your willingness to trust

00:42.770 --> 00:44.680
your companions with your lives.

00:45.190 --> 00:46.900
That means we'll need people.

00:47.650 --> 00:49.050
I know a place we could go.

00:50.340 --> 00:51.770
You can't mean...

