03:45.860 --> 03:51.000
<i>They moved their base here, to Susukino, 
in search of more difficult raids.</i>

03:51.970 --> 03:55.980
<i>Which means that no one's 
paying attention to them.</i>

03:56.800 --> 03:59.500
<i>Right now, he's the only one I can ask.</i>

04:00.800 --> 04:03.550
I've come with a request for you,

04:04.080 --> 04:05.550
as the Silver Sword guild master.

04:05.550 --> 04:07.050
Understood. I'm in.

04:08.150 --> 04:12.810
