to hear what he wanted?

04:17.490 --> 04:18.530
Thanks.

04:19.000 --> 04:19.990
Well?

04:19.990 --> 04:21.650
I'm requesting your participation in a full raid.

04:22.270 --> 04:26.750
In a new raid zone at the lowest 
level of the Depths of Palm.

04:27.520 --> 04:31.690
It's a full raid, so only twenty-four 
adventurers can go in at once.

04:32.330 --> 04:34.660
We can't rely on numbers.

04:35.050 --> 04:37.170
Then we'll have to go in to investigate it.

04:37.560 --> 04:39.050
Already done.

04:39.570 --> 04:40.350
Oh?

04:43.040 --> 04:44.390
Look at this!

04:44.390 --> 04:46.030
What a surprise.

04:46.030 --> 04:47.430
That's enough for today.

04:47.430 --> 04:48.400
Let's go back.

04:48.400 --> 04:49.330
Right on.

04:50.220 --> 04:53.260
Oh, my... There are monsters everywhere.

04:50.750 --> 04:56.180
