04:56.630 --> 04:59.190
I believe it will be extremely difficult.

04:59.190 --> 05:00.740
What types of enemies?

05:01.240 --> 05:03.360
The ones we saw were slimes.

05:03.910 --> 05:05.700
More than five meters in diameter.

05:06.410 --> 05:08.500
The rest is only my guess,

05:08.500 --> 05:12.280
but given the layout of the facility 
and the legends surrounding it,

05:12.280 --> 05:15.050
I believe there's a large monster, 
either a giant or a phantom beast.

05:15.050 --> 05:17.460
A giant? Convenient.

05:18.090 --> 05:21.230
We're based in Susukino, so we're used to them.

05:21.780 --> 05:24.290
