05:27.520 --> 05:29.550
Have you ever been to Susukino?

05:29.550 --> 05:31.120
Yes, a few times.

05:31.120 --> 05:34.730
I'd heard it had gotten dangerous 
after the Apocalypse.

05:35.050 --> 05:38.310
Silver Sword's presence here is a big help.

05:38.310 --> 05:41.050
Nothing like having a well-ordered 
combat guild around.

05:41.450 --> 05:44.240
They aren't thugs like Brigandia.

05:45.040 --> 05:49.240
I suppose those thugs must have 
wandered off somewhere.

05:49.690 --> 05:51.700
What do you mean, problems?

05:51.700 --> 05:54.500
Right now, we're shut down.

05:55.240 --> 05:56.790
We don't have enough people.

05:57.900 --> 06:01.270
Some members couldn't keep up with the raids.

06:01.270 --> 06:03.020
And some people are still in the guild,

06:03.020 --> 06:06.060
but they don't want to participate 
in any more large-scale fights.

06:06.060 --> 06:07.760
In other words, they've retired.

06:08.370 --> 06:10.710
They could do an easy raid,

06:10.710 --> 06:12.760
but not a really rough one.

06:13.220 --> 06:15.100
