06:15.100 --> 06:20.270
We're up to level 95, but we can 
only take twenty people at most.

06:21.100 --> 06:23.840
Is that because of your memories?

06:25.130 --> 06:28.780
Oh, that story about how if you 
die, you lose your memories?

06:29.290 --> 06:31.990
We don't believe idle gossip like that.

06:32.270 --> 06:34.010
We aren't scared or anything, either.

06:34.540 --> 06:36.040
Then why?

06:36.760 --> 06:39.040
How many times have you died since then?

06:39.440 --> 06:41.530
Since the Apocalypse?

06:42.160 --> 06:43.420
No, not once.

06:44.450 --> 06:46.920
I can't explain it to someone 
who doesn't understand.

06:48.670 --> 06:50.770
When you die, you learn a lot...

06:51.410 --> 06:54.430
That you suck, that you're petty, that you're lame.

06:55.060 --> 06:57.540
If you die a hundred times, 
you learn that a hundred times.

06:57.540 --> 06:59.440
It gets too painful to continue.

07:07.090 --> 07:09.700
