09:04.620 --> 09:07.230
I'm a bright star, shining in the night sky!

09:07.230 --> 09:10.480
I'm the pretty-girl galactic idol, Tetra!

09:11.330 --> 09:12.990
Call me "Tetra"!

09:13.220 --> 09:14.330
Tetra, huh?

09:15.150 --> 09:16.990
I guess you're cute,

09:15.640 --> 09:16.470
Wink!

09:16.990 --> 09:19.740
