16:13.330 --> 16:14.170
You little...

16:14.170 --> 16:15.600
That's a warrior's life!

16:15.600 --> 16:16.760
Wait!

16:18.020 --> 16:19.130
Hey!

16:19.780 --> 16:22.550
You guys really aren't worried, are you?

16:22.550 --> 16:24.580
We're just happy-go-lucky. That's all.

16:26.730 --> 16:29.340
Looks like he hasn't changed, though.

16:29.610 --> 16:32.010
Honestly, that worries me.

16:32.420 --> 16:34.570
But he came to the raid.

16:34.570 --> 16:35.850
I'm sure he'll understand.

16:36.680 --> 16:39.550
The other idiots and I did.

16:39.550 --> 16:43.370
And if he can't, he simply isn't that good.

16:44.540 --> 16:46.590
I can't wait!

16:46.590 --> 16:49.610
I can't wait to rip things apart.

16:49.940 --> 16:52.370
I hope we can finish it up this year.

16:52.370 --> 16:53.610
Yeah.

16:54.200 --> 16:58.370
There are all kinds of events around New Year's.

16:58.370 --> 17:03.370
<b>26 Days Until Christmas</b>

16:59.800 --> 17:01.120
I see.

17:01.120 --> 17:03.370
Sounds like you're having a rough time, Naotsugu.

17:03.600 --> 17:04.760
Yeah.

17:04.760 --> 17:06.320
You okay?

17:06.320 --> 17:08.540
That was the guy who was chasing Serara, right?

17:08.540 --> 17:10.680
That demi-glace guy.

17:10.680 --> 17:12.130
It's Demikas.

17:12.290 --> 17:15.690
Well, William has an eye on him, so he'll be fine.

17:15.690 --> 17:18.800
And his People of the Land wife 
has him on a leash, too.

17:18.800 --> 17:21.180
Really? That's hilarious.

17:22.900 --> 17:23.650
Oops.

17:23.950 --> 17:25.760
How about food?

17:25.760 --> 17:27.570
Are you eating nutritious stuff?

17:27.570 --> 17:29.160
You want chicken, right?

17:29.160 --> 17:32.220
It's crispy outside, and juicy inside!

17:32.220 --> 17:34.940
In winter, chicken is delicious!

17:34.940 --> 17:37.120
You're sure pushing chicken hard.

17:37.560 --> 17:39.170
Well, you know...

17:39.170 --> 17:41.660
Only twenty-six days until Christmas, right?

17:41.660 --> 17:42.660
Yeah.

17:42.990 --> 17:46.410
I just hope you can get back by then.

17:46.710 --> 17:48.670
Well, you know...

17:49.360 --> 17:51.700
I'll try my best, okay?

17:52.940 --> 17:53.860
Bye.

17:54.200 --> 17:57.070
Yeah, talk to you tomorrow.

17:58.890 --> 18:01.680
Marie!

18:01.960 --> 18:04.480
Having a cozy telepathy chat at a time like this?

18:04.480 --> 18:06.180
Are you supposed to be a drama heroine?

18:06.180 --> 18:10.190
Are you eventually going to say, 
"Which is more important? Me or your work?"

18:10.430 --> 18:12.850
Your imagination's a bit too active.

18:13.590 --> 18:18.680
We don't know where Minami's spies might be.

18:18.680 --> 18:20.500
That's why we put strict rules in place

18:20.500 --> 18:22.850
for talking with Shiroe and 
the others via telepathy.

18:22.850 --> 18:24.040
And yet...

18:24.040 --> 18:25.590
I know.

18:26.210 --> 18:31.480
That's why the two of us decided to only 
talk once a day, at 9:00 at night.

18:31.960 --> 18:34.070
Huh? Huh?

18:34.070 --> 18:36.120
You don't need to say "Huh?" twice.

18:36.120 --> 18:38.320
We're only discussing basic stuff.

18:38.320 --> 18:40.870
I don't even know where Naotsugu is.

18:41.580 --> 18:42.970
So you know?

18:44.070 --> 18:46.960
They're about to start a raid, right?

18:46.960 --> 18:48.540
It's live or die.

18:48.540 --> 18:49.760
Well, they won't die...

18:49.760 --> 18:52.610
They won't die, but they need a break, right?

18:53.180 --> 18:55.090
I'm not going to get in their way.

18:55.090 --> 18:59.610
It's also my job to be the liaison between 
the Crescent Moon Alliance and them.

19:00.380 --> 19:02.620
I-It's work... Work.

19:03.260 --> 19:06.440
Liaison, huh? Sure.

19:06.440 --> 19:08.120
It's fine! Right?

19:08.390 --> 19:11.380
Really, Marie, you're so...

19:11.820 --> 19:14.130
I think I'm full, too.

19:14.130 --> 19:15.600
I'm sure.

19:16.570 --> 19:19.130
You just ate, right?

19:22.440 --> 19:25.890
Why do I feel so defeated?

19:35.780 --> 19:37.400
You stay here in Akihabara, Akatsuki.

19:38.830 --> 19:41.490
I need to ask a favor that only you can do.

19:43.540 --> 19:45.770
I want you to protect Princess Lenessia.

19:49.400 --> 19:52.710
<i>There are spies from Minami in Akihabara.</i>

19:53.540 --> 19:55.890
<i>The princess might be in danger,</i>

19:55.890 --> 19:57.210
<i>so I am to protect her.</i>

19:57.820 --> 19:59.180
<i>I understand that.</i>

19:59.590 --> 20:00.220
<i>But...</i>

20:01.230 --> 20:04.220
<i>I think his real goal is something else.</i>

20:06.480 --> 20:07.420
Um...

20:08.110 --> 20:09.890
What is that?

20:09.890 --> 20:10.980
A red bean bun.

20:11.290 --> 20:12.580
Red bean bun?

20:12.970 --> 20:15.480
Then, what are you drinking?

20:16.340 --> 20:17.480
Roasted green tea.

20:18.050 --> 20:20.490
Apple tea isn't to your taste?

20:20.820 --> 20:23.740
Everyone knows red bean buns 
are best with roasted green tea.

20:24.640 --> 20:25.580
Ah...

20:28.470 --> 20:29.930
I don't understand.

20:29.930 --> 20:31.250
It's difficult, isn't it?

20:32.360 --> 20:35.910
It's been a long time since I came to this town.

20:35.910 --> 20:38.510
But there are still so many 
things I don't understand.

20:38.770 --> 20:42.030
How adventurers think, their customs...

20:44.440 --> 20:46.510
This is just my personal taste.

20:46.800 --> 20:48.710
There's nothing wrong with apple tea.

20:50.260 --> 20:53.020
Thank you for your kindness.

20:55.180 --> 20:57.020
<i>This is a hard job...</i>

21:08.910 --> 21:11.410
<b>Amenoma</b>

21:17.140 --> 21:18.290
Welcome.

21:20.500 --> 21:25.210
<i>Powerful phantasm-level items can 
only be acquired through raids.</i>

21:25.210 --> 21:27.300
<i>Like my lord's griffon.</i>

21:27.980 --> 21:31.050
<i>They're proof that you've survived a 
difficult battle with your friends.</i>

21:29.540 --> 21:35.800
<b>Graupel Sword Byakumaru</b>

21:31.550 --> 21:34.310
<i>I've never done a raid.</i>

21:32.040 --> 21:35.800
<b>Screaming Sword Haganemushi</b>

21:35.010 --> 21:40.380
<i>So the only weapons I can get for 
this class are those that I can buy.</i>

21:40.830 --> 21:41.660
<i>But...</i>

21:42.530 --> 21:48.330
<b>Tatara 
Race/ Dwarf 
Samurai, Lv. 90 
Amenoma</b>

21:43.030 --> 21:46.330
Just so we're clear, I don't haggle.

21:47.130 --> 21:48.330
It's a pain.

21:50.830 --> 21:53.080
<b>Graupel Sword Byakumaru</b>

21:51.100 --> 21:53.080
<b>Effect/ Graupel Sword Byakumaru
