21:51.470 --> 21:53.080
<b>Price/ Graupel Sword Byakumaru
118,000 gold
Not Enough Gold</b>

21:53.810 --> 21:56.080
<i>It's twice the value of everything I own!</i>

21:58.860 --> 22:00.720
<i>I want to be stronger...</i>

22:04.810 --> 22:08.640
So this is the lowest level of the Depths of Palm...

22:09.050 --> 22:10.970
I had no idea there was a zone like this.

22:11.450 --> 22:13.730
This door really doesn't need to be that big.

22:13.730 --> 22:15.680
It's in here, right, Shiroe?

22:15.680 --> 22:16.540
Yeah.

22:16.540 --> 22:17.730
It's finally time.

22:19.050 --> 22:20.460
<i>Shiroe...</i>

22:20.460 --> 22:24.990
<i>I don't know what you're after, 
but I won't let it happen.</i>

22:25.860 --> 22:29.480
<i>I'll rip apart all your wishes!</i>

22:29.860 --> 22:34.650
<i>I'll change that stupid smirk of yours into a sob.</i>

24:06.050 --> 24:07.480
In the lowest level

24:07.480 --> 24:10.600
of the Depths of Palm lies the 
raid zone, the Abyssal Shaft.

24:10.600 --> 24:12.700
There, the full raid finally begins.

24:12.700 --> 24:14.680
As the fierce battle rages,

24:14.680 --> 24:19.020
Shiroe, William, and Demikas fight with 
their own thoughts in their hearts.

24:19.020 --> 24:22.780
And in distant Akihabara, Akatsuki is uncertain.

24:23.270 --> 24:25.250
Next time: The Abyssal Shaft.

24:23.270 --> 24:29.940
<b>The Abyssal Shaft</b>

24:25.800 --> 24:27.770
Rise up once more.
